{"tid":2295390,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"「香港一定發達」樓市大好友沽樓套現","createTime":"2020-11-21T18:05:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T18:12:20.000Z","uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"20b1420b2d52458f2add7f610ee2254fbe2ba770","tid":2295390,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T18:05:30.000Z","msg":"第四波疫情殺到，樓市形勢再度轉弱，樓市大好友都沽樓套現。市場消息指，向來睇好香港樓市的行政會議前成員林奮強，近日以2,768萬元售出其持有16年的大埔聚豪天下單號洋房，是他近年第二次賣樓套現。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201121/TJ3QVKELBJD3DBXPURVGI3VJEM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201121%2FTJ3QVKELBJD3DBXPURVGI3VJEM%2F&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5r%2FS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=bda0315c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201121%2FTJ3QVKELBJD3DBXPURVGI3VJEM%2F&h=5a22facc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201121/TJ3QVKELBJD3DBXPURVGI3VJEM/</a>"},{"pid":"6e791353a7b0fc1c599e00e9334d1d1856e937a9","tid":2295390,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T18:05:55.000Z","msg":"租樓日日歉"},{"pid":"3e2727311d09ffe0a56751757c9691d0202e6d87","tid":2295390,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T18:08:33.000Z","msg":"想走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10752dccb4db9ecac30accb6519ae30537463c2b","tid":2295390,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3e2727311d09ffe0a56751757c9691d0202e6d87","tid":2295390,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T18:08:33.000Z","msg":"想走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T18:10:25.000Z","msg":"翻查資料，政府於2012年10年宣佈實施買家印花稅（BSD）及加強版額外印花稅（SSD）。而林奮強於2012年6月獲委任為行會成員，隨後宣佈會放售三至五個物業，作為未來五年的生活開支，其後早於10月加辣前，放售西半山寶華軒14B及14C單位，被廣泛報道<span class=\"red\">「偷步賣樓」</span>，其後廉署正式立案調查林奮強賣樓事件，最終林向特首提出休假請求。"},{"pid":"46621e0770326df12e9fa24de25c99bcfa30c657","tid":2295390,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T18:12:20.000Z","msg":"趁港樓港股呢排彈一彈 好走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />星期一準備去CUT左個月供PLAN"}]}